<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1957-12-19T20:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1955-02-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="250" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d250">
                        <head>250. Editorial Note</head>
                        <p>Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_DAW1">Dulles</persName> left
                            Paris on May 6, 1957. The Ambassadors continued their discussions until
                            May 8, but no record of their meetings has been found in Department of
                            State files.</p>
